text: Moaaz Mohamed Ibrahim (born February 8, 1999) is a Qatari athlete, specializing in the discus throw. He won the gold medal at 2016 IAAF World U20 Championships. ==Personal bests== {| class=wikitable |- !Event !Notes !Venue !Date |- | discus throw || 63,63 m || 2016 IAAF World U20 Championships || 24 July 2016 |} ==References== ==External links== * Mohamed Ibrahim Moaaz at OmRiyadat English * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Qatari male discus throwers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Qatar
